{"tid":1801824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟圈]唔止小店 要有黃色企業","createTime":"2019-12-29T03:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T05:08:04.000Z","uid":35136,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f519eae16fd60f412643893503d35ff451ebb241","tid":1801824,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"而家黃色經濟圈嘅模式不利擴充<br />\n大家湧去某幾間出名嘅小店 而間舖就消化唔到咁多人 排長龍個畫面好靚 但其實係唔理想<br />\n舖頭消化唔切 實際都唔係賺多好多<br />\n顧客要等好耐 浪費time cost <br />\n同時門檻高 好多淺黃人唔會同你排<br />\n而且其實威脅唔大 因為個市場佔有率低<br />\n但其實我哋一直忽略咗黃色企業<br />\nHKTVmall<br />\n王維基有去中大保衛戰<br />\n壹傳媒<br />\n唔使講啦<br />\n大班<br />\n太子爺撐抗爭被中國封殺 金企業<br />\n大快活<br />\n杜生被中國封殺都照請做代言人<br />\n<br />\n幫襯佢哋門檻低<br />\n好多分店容易消化黃人嘅購買力<br />\n容易集資擴充去搶市場<br />\n所以文宣方向要令更多淺黃幫襯黃企業 甚至投資落去"},{"pid":"18125a28b5b138ae27cdd3de6c21616430f4a307","tid":1801824,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16d77673494df98fb7f83f9ab22c85c1ef7e79e0","tid":1801824,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"蕭生都冇？"},{"pid":"edaa71f716e81334195ddd1fa08002795ff5d336","tid":1801824,"uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16d77673494df98fb7f83f9ab22c85c1ef7e79e0","tid":1801824,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"蕭生都冇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"一時好rough咁出呢個post<br />\n大家可以補充"},{"pid":"97b194caad4deaf661a09e718a3c40181e82d24d","tid":1801824,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7279633de4d99decdfc1ae7c117721781ad16ff7","tid":1801824,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigx