ce428714f2ad4a65a478cee","tid":1801824,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:00:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Google Map</span></span>好多人用<br />\n<br />\n大家可以係黃店影多d靚相<br />\nPost上 google map<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留中/英文評語<br />\n介紹俾本地人和世界各地旅客<br />\n推廣黃店<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n====================<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n【和你食】九龍區 - 中餐/茶記篇 - post你食過的黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799551</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"30720210a001ec5e2084ddd8d5f7c30f66569384","tid":1801824,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51cc322d79ad7b2229e475161f139fb12e031a1f","tid":1801824,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"仲有光時啊喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"當然冇唔記得光時<br />\n但始終光時暫時規模太細<br />\n就係消化唔到啲購買力<br />\n訂咗貨要幾星期先到<br />\n未擴張到咁上下嘅規模之前要令淺黃知道唔想等咁耐可以去HKTVmall"},{"pid":"bd76e149cc0cf2f6e1f2ed793fbdd46757e401a7","tid":1801824,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30720210a001ec5e2084ddd8d5f7c30f66569384","tid":1801824,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51cc322d79ad7b2229e475161f139fb12e031a1f","tid":1801824,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"仲有光時啊喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"當然冇唔記得光時<br />\n但始終光時暫時規模太細<br />\n就係消化唔到啲購買力<br />\n訂咗貨要幾星期先到<br />\n未擴張到咁上下嘅規模之前要令淺黃知道唔想等咁耐可以去HKTVmall"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"HKTVmall都okay<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af60ab756ff711a8a92560602c863b6aa29362c","tid":1801824,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"點解無人推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5c227b6a9afeb196c14ede5f110c820099a085","tid":1801824,"uid":85396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:08:04.000Z","msg":"大班唔係跪左加割席咩？<br />\n<br />\n【Kelly Online】疑轉發譏諷「藍絲」警察帖文網民籲罷買 大班西餅太子爺急道歉<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-02 10:24<br />\n<br />\n￼郭勇維隨後刪文道歉。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n￼fb截圖<br />\n<br />\n大班麵包西餅公司創辦人之子郭勇維，疑於社交網站轉載譏諷「藍絲」和香港警察的帖文，為此舉惹怒不少內地網民，更呼籲罷買。郭勇維隨後刪文道歉，大班麵包西餅亦回應稱郭的個人言論不代表公司。<br />\n<br />\n郭勇維在其個人facebook轉發多則貼文，譏諷支持政府和警察的市民「無腦」的貼文，有網民將有關轉發截圖，隨即惹來不少內地網民的不滿，甚至呼籲罷買。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">郭勇維隨後刪文道歉，稱有關言論只是個人分享，與公司無關，「若有關言論或資訊引起誤會或冒犯任何人，本人就此作出道歉。」大班麵包西餅也迅速與郭勇維「割席」，稱郭勇維只屬幾十位董事之一，強調郭的個人言論不代表公司。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不過淘寶及天貓等網上購物平台現在已經搜索不到大班麵包西餅的店舖，淘寶上的大班西餅旗艦店早前亦已關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource ： 頭條日報（慎入）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1581765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1581765&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=7992edd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1581765</a>"}]}